i## Using Build Args		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iIn a Dockerfile, use the ARG command to define a build argument, which		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ican be used like environment variables defined by ENV:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
